NODE_ID: contact_silas
LOCATION: kaelens_hab
CHARACTERS: Narrator, Silas
DESCRIPTION: """
You kill the connection with Anya and switch to a secure, untraceable channel. After three rings, a burst of static answers, followed by a raspy, paranoid voice. "Who is this?"

It's Silas. He went dark years ago after the Sterling Tower incident. You tell him you need information on ghost signals in Gamma-7.

Silas: "You're playing with fire, Kaelen. That place... they left things buried there. Things that shouldn't be woken up. If you have to go, meet me. The Glitch. One hour. Come alone." The line goes dead.
"""
