NODE_ID: the_glitch_bar
LOCATION: the_glitch
CHARACTERS: Narrator, Silas
DESCRIPTION: """
The Glitch is a dive bar where data-brokers and code-slicers trade secrets over fizzing glasses of synthetic alcohol. Silas is hunched in a corner booth, looking older and more frayed than you remember. He slides a small, metallic object across the table—a chroniton nullifier.

Silas: "Whatever is making that signal... it's not from around here. They called it 'Project Chimera.' Don't let the Bureau know what you find. And don't try to shut it down. Use this instead. It will stabilize the field, show you what's really there. Now get out of here before they see us."
"""
